{"tid":1427610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"試著不要說\"屌你老母唔好影相!\"， 試著說\"拜託影還影唔好影大頭\"","createTime":"2019-08-07T06:58:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T16:01:47.000Z","uid":143499,"like":68,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"269ecd582e01eca92d8ee8bf3a09bb8dd833b8a6","tid":1427610,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:58:49.000Z","msg":"大家英文水平唔會差過毅進仔<br />\n<br />\n試著不要說 no photo！<br />\n<br />\n試著說&quot; please don't zoom-in protesters' face, because they are facing unfair judgement&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下下屌老母，就算支持你都反感啦<br />\n<br />\n好多鬼佬純粹想影相同朋友講發生緊乜嘢事，喺外國影示威者好平常因為人哋面對公平審判， 嘗試下同佢哋詳細解釋點解唔好影大頭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記錄真相係人哋嘅自由"},{"pid":"efcc6b722970de60510ad70bb900521e5c2d879e","tid":1427610,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:01:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5c73c231db0b45dbe2ffaae7997c641ab88044","tid":1427610,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:01:38.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"f79bfa84adce18ce18a5138dbd6f679464b67a4a","tid":1427610,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d5c73c231db0b45dbe2ffaae7997c641ab88044","tid":1427610,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:01:38.000Z","msg":"pish"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:02:53.000Z","msg":"thx, need more pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d62fdc8aab7a4eb8ebf7be1b08a433333b668ab1","tid":1427610,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:04:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab57543d06875d8ae68ea123dd2787709fbafce","tid":1427610,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:06:07.000Z","msg":"true"},{"pid":"8d542d93ef14d19e1afd8ebd41cb24b231120265","ti